\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\">泰利 &middot; 路易威登主要事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p><br />\n係舊登扮絕症，獲得一眾巴絲同情後就扮慘眾籌呃錢加呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舊登有紀錄但已經開唔返，以前line/ig都叫Terry2500，好多巴絲表示當年d人幾百一千咁捐比佢，自己追po睇返。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdtqxpB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdtqxpB.png&h=70b0526d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiLHvOQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiLHvOQ.png&h=47e1b27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbz9aOX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffbz9aOX.png&h=160440ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">舊登巴絲上水爆料</span><br />\n[/quote]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2348292/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2348292/page/1</a><br />\n#17開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwD9wcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwD9wcR.jpg&h=d6c58174&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wox2RcR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwox2RcR.jpg&h=6ed3b84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母當年話自己每分每秒d骨都痛到好似比火燒咁 又話自己有玻璃骨 行路都會腳斷 生活好大負擔呃咗幾撚多巴絲金錢同時間上嘅慰藉<br />\n見係絲打就流曬口水 打電話嚟傾一陣就問人係咪處女 <br />\n又話自己因為病冇女 日日就呻冇女冇女冇女<br />\n叫人入屯門探你唔肯就屌鳩人 話人唔重視你 鳩痕就認啦<br />\n同你好撚熟咩仆街 又話就死 7年啦 死撚左去邊呀？還錢先啦<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"purple\">泰利公爵(身價1x-20萬)富豪生活曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></p><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xWo2zGn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxWo2zGn.png&h=31d5e82e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMe5xs6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMe5xs6.png&h=5c223097&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3JxWUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3JxWUS.png&h=5d9199c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5Y20Gw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5Y20Gw.png&h=2e4fb882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBDeROi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBDeROi.png&h=85a861bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yWb0NmK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyWb0NmK.png&h=ad48f73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\">同場加映泰利公爵居住嘅電線外露公屋豪宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtNR2ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtNR2ee.png&h=8f729dde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tb3RhNA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTb3RhNA.png&h=0a194926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好豪華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有豪華三門大雪櫃、和式簡約小餐桌、意大利真皮梳化、各大名牌紙袋形咕𠱸、名貴多功能煮食鍋，另加電線外露，好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"purple\"><span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\">泰利公爵鼓勵人心小故事</p></span></span><br />\n藉住同街市呀姐嘅對話經驗去創作買名牌袋嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有巴絲指出名店sa根本唔會咁同客講野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C38xWWK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC38xWWK.png&h=c0807374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身價過1x萬嘅泰利公爵紆尊降貴坐係公屋地板補鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F2Dqxvb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF2Dqxvb.png&h=0e5d81ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">      terry 你mon得咁實，請回應<br />\n1. 幾年前，聲稱有病有絕症，要人捐錢，又要絲打陪你，但成日聊絲打講淫野，成件事係點解釋？成件事係唔係想騙財騙色？<br />\n2. 點解會忽然富貴，由捐錢醫病，去到事業有成，白手興家，上網炫富？錢從何來？係唔係人地捐比你？<br />\n3. 不斷係ig 度follow 幾千條女，鍥而不捨咁不斷dm d女仔，長達幾年，會唔會覺得自己行為有侵犯性？<br />\n4. 運動期間入文宣Group 借d 意約女手足出黎痴身痴勢，可唔可以解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n請正面回應，不要龜縮<br />\n以上完全理性討論，唔好屈我係hater<br />\n跟住扮睇唔到<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ce67d34e480b6ed3e557a77ff54f9b2ec4ba64f","tid":2451403,"uid":248020,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qk9ehRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQk9ehRy.png&h=fe9562f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"844a0d84bfba99e922b8cdbd013909d9b2bcd15f","tid":2451403,"uid":259963,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"慢左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTerry哥解封ig啦<br />\n我無曬人生樂趣啦"},{"pid":"49b7492ad0e858d8265adf47c93d60fc8441f97a","tid":2451403,"uid":317228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"咁都有女會信，d女自己都淫同蠢啦"},{"pid":"e4117b2bd60aef9b5a335d2802a15d15b30ab296","tid":2451403,"uid":301529,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T05:30:03.000Z","msg":"冇野玩嚕"},{"pid":"d56776fa287202583f225e427b78a8abe9aef0b2","tid":2451403,"uid":350686,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-1